##  Parámetros

| Parámetro | Valor |
|---|---|
| Versión IKE | IKEv2 |
| PSK | `Cisco12345` (wildcard) |
| Cifrado IPSec | AES-256 |
| Hash IPSec | SHA-256 |
| Modo IPSec | **Transport** |
| Protocolo Túnel | mGRE (multipoint GRE) |
| NHRP Network-ID | 100 |
| NHRP Auth | `nhrpkey` |
| Subred DMVPN | 10.0.0.0/24 |
| Enrutamiento | EIGRP AS 100 |
| HUB extra | `ip nhrp redirect` |
| SPOKE extra | `ip nhrp shortcut` |

