##  Verificación

### Ver estado DMVPN
```cisco
show dmvpn
```

### Ver NHRP — shortcut routes
```cisco
show ip nhrp
```
Después del primer ping Spoke-to-Spoke aparece:
```
10.0.0.3/32 via 10.0.0.3
  Type: dynamic  Flags: router nhop   ← shortcut instalada
```

### Ver vecinos EIGRP
```cisco
show ip eigrp neighbor
```

### Ver rutas EIGRP — ANTES del primer ping
```cisco
show ip route eigrp
```
```
D    10.10.3.0/24 [90/...] via 10.0.0.1   ← via HUB
```

### Ver rutas EIGRP — DESPUÉS del primer ping
```cisco
show ip route eigrp
```
```
D    10.10.3.0/24 [90/...] via 10.0.0.3   ← via SPOKE2 directo ✅
```

### Ver SA IKEv2
```cisco
show crypto ikev2 sa
```

### Ver paquetes cifrados
```cisco
show crypto ipsec sa | include encaps|decaps
```

### Ping spoke a spoke
```
PC1> ping 10.10.3.100 repeat 10
```

